CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, May 11, 1957, pg. A13 reads: " Delta Patronesses And Chairman - Ethel Ramos Harris, left, general chairman of the Delta Sigma Theta Regional here last week-end, chats with Delta Patroness Board president, Mrs. Frances Primas, and Mrs. Helen Dendridge at the tea given Sunday at the Greene Hearthe [sic] by Miss Nancy Lee. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of Ethel Ramos Harris, Frances Primas, and Helen Dendridge, posed for Delta Sigma Theta tea in the Greene Hearth
